OL,3,CPolice fear rapid rise in deaths from
OL,4,Cnew super-strength opioid in Wales
OL,6,FA Welsh police force chief says there
OL,7,Fis a risk that deaths involving
OL,8,Fnitazenes - a new deadly drug - could
OL,9,Frise "exponentially" over the coming
OL,10,Fweeks and months.
OL,12,FSixteen deaths related to the have
OL,13,Fbeen recorded in the and force areas
OL,14,Fsince December 2023.
OL,16,FIn an exclusive interview with ITV
OL,17,FWales, South Wales Police has now told
OL,18,Fus they are becoming increasingly
OL,19,Fworried about the spread of the drug,
OL,20,Fwhich can be far stronger than opioids
OL,21,Flike fentanyl, heroin and morphine.
