OL,3,CPolice fear rapid rise in deaths from
OL,4,Cnew super-strength opioid in Wales
OL,6,FThere are worries that nitazenes are
OL,7,Fbeing disguised as over-the-counter
OL,8,Fmedicine and then sold on the black
OL,9,Fmarket.
OL,11,FIt comes after a recent ITV Wales
OL,12,Finvestigation revealed that health
OL,13,Fofficials are "severely concerned"
OL,14,Fabout the influx of the drug.
OL,16,FDetective Superintendent Mark Lewis
OL,17,Fsays they "just don't know where this
OL,18,Fis going to go", in relation to the
OL,19,Fnumber of deaths related to nitazenes
OL,20,Frising.
