OL,6,FHe said: "That's the honest answer.
OL,7,FThere is a risk this could increase
OL,8,Fexponentially other the weeks and
OL,9,Fmonths to come.
OL,11,F"Our challenge is to keep working hard
OL,12,Fwith our partners to try and prevent
OL,13,Fthat, to get the message out.
OL,15,F"But there is a real risk that could
OL,16,Fhappen. I would encourage users who
OL,17,Fare worried to link in with their
OL,18,Fsupport agencies.
